a run. cried in the shower.

757
00:53:14.925 --> 00:53:17.019
The minute I was alone
for two seconds. I cried.

758
00:53:17.594 --> 00:53:18.721
I couldn't sleep.

759
00:53:19.763 --> 00:53:22.062
I was afraid to be alone
in the house with the kids.

760
00:53:22.132 --> 00:53:23.259
I was afraid...

761
