780
00:54:24.328 --> 00:54:25.591
That's what it was like.

781
00:54:26.997 --> 00:54:28.124
I got through it.

782
00:54:30.901 --> 00:54:32.479
I made it through. and
I'm more proud of that

783
00:54:32.503 --> 00:54:35.940
