and we had all these
kids. and we were fighting.

788
00:54:53.323 --> 00:54:54.868
I would look at you
sometimes and I would think.

789
00:54:54.892 --> 00:54:56.622
"One day. this is
gonna be worth it.

790
00:54:58.428 --> 00:55:02.524
One day. I'm gonna dance
with him at Whitney's wedding.

791
00:55:02.599 --> 00:55:06.161
And we will have built...

792
00:55:07.604 --> 00:55:10.130
